
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-fang-core-coap-pubsub-failure-detection-00.txt'>
    <title>"Failure Detection Extensions for Publish-Subscribe in CoAP", Luyuan Fang</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-fang-core-coap-pubsub-failure-detection-00.txt</link>
    <description>This document defines extensions to the Constrained Application Protocol Publish/Subscribe function set, to make the protocol suitable to address the use case of failure detection in a hyper- scale system with millions of endpoints. Specifically, this document defines a Last Will mechanism and a scheme to guarantee hot fail-over of the pub/sub broker.</description>
    <dc:date>2016-03-21T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
